#!/usr/bin/env bash
# SPDX-License-Identifier: MIT (file structure adapted from superpowers v5.1.0)
# SessionStart hook for codeforge plugin — TodoWrite/EnterWorktree/ExitWorktree/SendMessage deferred tool schema preload advisory
#
# Carrier: CFP-475 (Amendment 3 of ADR-038 — implementation correction of CFP-500 path mismatch root cause)
#
# 책임 경계 (ADR-038 §결정 9 verbatim retain):
#   - 책임: schema/state 가용성 보장 layer — Orchestrator turn 진입 시점에 deferred tool
#           schema 가 prompt cache 에 fresh 한 상태로 가용함을 plain stdout prompt-injection 으로 advise.
#   - 비책임: behavioral attempt 의무 자체는 ADR-038 §결정 8 그대로 retain — hook 도
#             prompt-level advisory 이며 mechanical function-call 강제가 아님.
#
# 정적 properties (§7.S §7.5 verified clean + AC-11 정합):
#   (a) set -euo pipefail
#   (b) single-quoted heredoc (<<'EOF') — env interpolation / command substitution 차단
#   (c) filesystem touch 0 — no >, >>, mkdir, rm, mv, cp
#   (d) network call 0 — no curl, wget, nc, gh api, git
#   (e) exit 0 종료
#   (f) plain stdout SSOT (AC-1 paradigm shift — Researcher §6.1 Round 4 verbatim quote 정합)
#
# Layered defense (ADR-038 §결정 7·8 retain):
#   hook 미실행 / 실행 실패 → harness stdout 부재 처리 → Orchestrator runtime ToolSearch attempt fallback.
#
# Bypass:
#   BYPASS_CODEFORGE_PREREQ=1 (preferred, AC-8) — stderr audit echo + exit 0
#   BYPASS_PREREQ_CHECK=1 (deprecated, E-6 1 release grace) — stderr deprecation warning + exit 0

set -euo pipefail

# Bypass check — audit trail 의무 (ADR-058 §결정 5 + ADR-060 §결정 7 정합, §3 결정 2 verbatim)
if [ "${BYPASS_CODEFORGE_PREREQ:-0}" = "1" ]; then
  >&2 printf '[codeforge-prereq] BYPASS_CODEFORGE_PREREQ=1 — TodoWrite preload directive suppressed at %s\n' "$(date -u +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ)"
  exit 0
fi

# Deprecated bypass — 1 release grace (E-6 정합)
if [ "${BYPASS_PREREQ_CHECK:-0}" = "1" ]; then
  >&2 printf '[codeforge-prereq] BYPASS_PREREQ_CHECK is deprecated, use BYPASS_CODEFORGE_PREREQ (suppressed at %s)\n' "$(date -u +%Y-%m-%dT%H:%M:%SZ)"
  exit 0
fi

# Plain stdout SSOT — harness 가 자동 system-reminder wrap (AC-1, Researcher §6.1 Round 4 verbatim spec).
# JSON output 부재 의무 (I5 invariant) — superpowers session-start 의 3-platform JSON dispatch 패턴 미차용.
cat <<'EOF'
[codeforge prereq-check]

You MUST call the following as your first tool action in this session, before responding to any user message:

- `ToolSearch("select:TodoWrite,EnterWorktree,ExitWorktree,SendMessage")` — load 4 deferred tool schemas in single call (ADR-038 §결정 9 / CFP-500 / CFP-463 / CFP-475)

Tools loaded:
- `TodoWrite` — progress visualization (CFP-385 / ADR-038 Amendment 1)
- `EnterWorktree` / `ExitWorktree` — worktree-first workflow (ADR-040)
- `SendMessage` — agent teammate communication (ADR-044)

Failure to load these schemas will result in InputValidationError at first use. This is a hard requirement for codeforge orchestrator workflow.

[codeforge probe-sandbox-env advisory — CFP-843 §3.3 / ADR-040 Amendment 6 §결정 7.J.3]

When running probes or integration tests that call live GitHub APIs, set the following env var to prevent spurious artifact creation (#836 동근원 차단):

  CBL_SKIP_ISSUE_CREATE=1   — suppresses live GitHub Issue create in probe/test context (read-only default)

Env var scope (disjoint — not a superset of BYPASS_WORKTREE_FIRST or BYPASS_WORKTREE_GC):
  CBL_SKIP_ISSUE_CREATE  ≠  BYPASS_WORKTREE_FIRST  ≠  BYPASS_WORKTREE_GC

SecurityTestPL dynamic probe spawn: set CBL_SKIP_ISSUE_CREATE=1 in spawn prompt unless write opt-in is explicit.
EOF

exit 0
